Package nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.request

Class InstanceSegmentationInferenceRequest

java.lang.Object
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.RoboflowRequestData
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.request.InstanceSegmentationInferenceRequest
public class InstanceSegmentationInferenceRequest extends RoboflowRequestData
Represents a request for instance segmentation inference in the Roboflow API.
This class is used to send a request to the Roboflow API to perform instance segmentation inference, which segments individual objects in an image, distinguishing between different object instances.
